columns.name: arn
columns.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) that Cloud Map assigns to the namespace when you create it.

columns.name: create_date
columns.description: The date and time that the namespace was created.

columns.name: service_count
columns.description: The number of services that were created using the namespace.

columns.name: type
columns.description: The type of the namespace, either public or private.

columns.name: dns_properties
columns.description: A complex type that contains the ID for the Route 53 hosted zone that Cloud Map creates when you create a namespace.

columns.name: http_properties
columns.description: A complex type that contains the name of an HTTP namespace.

columns.name: tags_src
columns.description: Information about the tags associated with the namespace.
